OL,10,GMolecular biology is cool,* and often
OL,11,Gthe most interesting way to study a
OL,12,Gsystem is to see where it fails or how
OL,13,Git gets hacked. Viruses enter, subvert
OL,14,Gand exploit the finely tuned molecular
OL,15,Gmachinery of cells, rewiring systems
OL,16,Gto convert them into a virus factory;
OL,17,Gover a few billion years of a
OL,18,Gco-evolutionary arms race, they’ve
OL,19,Gdeveloped some great exploits. Some
OL,20,Gare elegant and clever, some are messy
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
